avy heart for weaks and coming home to the unknown had put an even heavier burden on her. Her body was tense and rigid, she needed to unwind. She ran a bath and was half naked when a knock came to her door.<br><br>She wrapped herself in her robe and opened the door. Her eyes lit up and a smile came to her face, "Hey, you!"<br><br>RS <br><br><br> Ilaenu Tru'Hael <br>51 Enchantress <br>ReveredRallos Zek <br><br><br><br>Message Edited on 06/29/01 10:56AM by Ilaenu  <br>  <br><br> RE: :::After months on the road, Reesey returns to Dane Manor... <br><br> <br>      Stonelor<br>Posted On 06/29/01 11:31AM <br><br><br>I am here brothers. and so are the Arcon Brothers. We will not leave but there must be strong leadership, I stand by you Desperate.<br><br><br>Xaneth Arcones<br>Wlall Arconos<br>Stonelor Arconas<br>Ricken Arconis<br>Eriss Arconxs <br><br>Stonelor Arconas<br>Hand of Dane Officer<br><br><br>Quote from Machiavelli <br>"There is nothing more difficult to take in hand, more perilous to conduct, or more uncertain in its success, than to take lead in the introduction of a new order of things." (from The Prince, 1532) <br>  <br><br> RE: :::The Rogues gather <br><br> <br>      Topasere<br>Posted On 06/29/01 12:12PM <br><br><br>::perched in a nearby tree Topa watched a fierce battle. once the battle had ended he saw Desdmona come sit under the tree to rest. "Have you gone to see your father the lunatic?"said Topa. Mona replied as she quickly turned to look at her guest, "HOW DARE YOU SAY.....Oh it's you." "What the HELL is going on??"Mona questioned still fierce from the fight as well as from her own thoughts. Topa tore a chunk out of the tree. "This tree is rotting." Mona replied" Every thing does" Topa smirked &amp; hopped down from the tree branch lighting his cigar along the way. <br><br>"Then why are you so disstraught??" Mona said "because I'm not thinking about a tree" Topa Replied, "What makes you think a guild is 